docs.lead_paragraph: Two police officers burst through a hotel room door with guns drawn, yelling "Police! Get Down!" just after an alleged money laundering transaction went down. But instead of briefcases stuffed with a drug dealer's cash, this exchange involved an undercover officer with supposedly stolen credit cards and the virtual currency bitcoin.

docs.abstract: Edward Rothstein Critic's Notebook; LBJ Presidential Library in Austin, Tex, as part of three-day gathering to commemorate 50th anniversary of Civil Rights Act, is promoting new assessment of Pres Lyndon Baines Johnson, showing him and Abraham Lincoln as kindred spirits.
